    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、正月早々仕事のメールか。先方も大変だなぁ\nえーっと、ⅢX宛のMV撮影日変更のお願い、か",
      "startTime": 8.4666666429,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.000182600001,
          "startTime": 7.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにfranさん達に連絡しないとな\n確か、年末聞いた時は――",
      "startTime": 18.9666666429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。ⅢXはお正月、三人ともオフを\n取るんですよね？　ゆっくり休んで下さいね",
      "startTime": 27.4666666429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、厳密には決めてないけど家でゆっくり過ごします\n漫画を読んだり……いや、まだ仕事があるわね",
      "startTime": 36.3302980585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "来年の『ERFOLG』の方針を決めないと。トレンド\n予測から需要のリサーチ……まだまだやること一杯だわ",
      "startTime": 45.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お正月も大変ですね。franさん、華やかな\nイメージですし、芸能人らしく海外旅行とか行くのかと",
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}